\c 27
\s UJakobe uzizuzela isibusiso kuIsaka
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi uIsaka esemdala lamehlo akhe esefiphele enga\add sa\add*boni\x + 48.10. 1 Sam. 3.2.\x*, wabiza uEsawu indodana yakhe enkulu, wathi kuye: Ndodana yami! Wasesithi kuye: Khangela ngi\add lapha\add*.
\v 2 Wasesithi: Khangela-ke, sengimdala, angilwazi usuku lokufa kwami.
\v 3 Ngakho khathesi, ake uthathe izikhali zakho, isikhwama sakho semitshoko ledandili lakho, uphume uye egangeni ungizingelele inyama yenyamazana\x + 25.27,28.\x*,
\v 4 ungilungisele ukudla okumnandi njengengikuthandayo, u\add ku\add*lethe kimi ukuthi ngidle, ukuze umphefumulo wami ukubusise ngingakafi\x + 48.9,15; 49.28. Dute. 33.1.\x*.
\p
\v 5 URebeka wasesizwa lapho uIsaka ekhuluma loEsawu indodana yakhe. UEsawu wasesiya egangeni ukuyazingela inyama yenyamazana ukuze ayilethe.
\v 6 URebeka wasekhuluma kuJakobe indodana yakhe, esithi: Khangela, ngizwile uyihlo ekhuluma kuEsawu umnewenu, esithi:
\v 7 Ngilethela inyama yenyamazana, ungilungisele ukudla okumnandi ukuthi ngidle, ngikubusise phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* ngingakafi.
\v 8 Ngakho khathesi, ndodana yami, lalela ilizwi lami kulokhu engikulaya khona\x + 27.13.\x*.
\v 9 Ake uye emhlanjini, ungithathele lapho amazinyane amabili amahle ezimbuzi, ngizawenzela uyihlo ukudla okumnandi njengalokho akuthandayo\x + 27.4.\x*;
\v 10 uza\add ku\add*sa-ke kuyihlo ukuthi adle, ukuze akubusise engakafi\x + 27.4.\x*.
\v 11 UJakobe wasesithi kuRebeka unina: Khangela, uEsawu umnewethu uyindoda elihwanqa\x + 25.25.\x*, kodwa ngiyindoda ebutshelezi.
\v 12 Mhlawumbe ubaba uzangiphulula\x + 27.21,22.\x*, besengisiba emehlweni akhe njengomhleka usulu, njalo ngizilethele isiqalekiso kungabi-ke yisibusiso.
\v 13 Unina wasesithi kuye: Isiqalekiso sakho kasibe phezu kwami\x + 1 Sam. 25.24. 2 Sam. 14.9. Mat. 27.25.\x*, ndodana yami; kuphela lalela ilizwi lami, uhambe ungithathele \add wona\add*.
\v 14 Wasehamba, wa\add wa\add*thatha, wa\add wa\add*letha kunina; unina waselungisa ukudla okumnandi njengalokho uyise akuthandayo\x + 27.4,9.\x*.
\v 15 URebeka wasethatha izigqoko ezinhle\f + \fk ezinhle: \fl Heb. \fq eziloyisekayo.\f* zikaEsawu indodana yakhe enkulu, ayelazo endlini, wagqokisa uJakobe indodana yakhe encinyane\x + 27.27.\x*;
\v 16 lezikhumba zamazinyane ezimbuzi wazifaka ezandleni zakhe lebutshelezini bentamo yakhe.
\v 17 Wasenika ukudla okumnandi lesinkwa ayekulungisile esandleni sikaJakobe indodana yakhe.
\p
\v 18 Wasesiza kuyise wathi: Baba! Wasesithi: Khangela ngi\add lapha\add*; ungubani ndodana yami?
\v 19 UJakobe wasesithi kuyise: NginguEsawu izibulo lakho; ngenze njengoba ungitshelile; ake uvuke uhlale, udle okwenyama yami yenyamazana, ukuze umphefumulo wakho ungibusise\x + 27.4.\x*.
\v 20 UIsaka wasesithi endodaneni yakhe: Kungani uyithole masinyane kangaka, ndodana yami? Wasesithi: Ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho yenze ukuthi ize phambi kwami\x + 24.12.\x*.
\v 21 UIsaka wasesithi kuJakobe: Ake usondele ukuze ngikuphulule\x + 27.12.\x*, ndodana yami, ukuthi uyindodana yami uEsawu uqobo, kumbe hatshi.
\v 22 UJakobe wasesondela kuIsaka uyise; wasemphulula wathi: Ilizwi liyilizwi likaJakobe, kodwa izandla ziyizandla zikaEsawu.
\v 23 Kodwa kamazanga ngoba izandla zakhe zaziloboya\x + 27.16.\x* njengezandla zomnewabo uEsawu; ngakho wambusisa.
\v 24 Wasesithi: Uyindodana yami uEsawu uqobo yini? Wasesithi: Ngi\add nguye\add*.
\v 25 Wasesithi: Sondeza kimi ukuze ngidle okwenyama yenyamazana yendodana yami, ukuze umphefumulo wami ukubusise\x + 27.4,10,19,31.\x*. Wase\add yi\add*sondeza kuye, wasesidla; waseletha kuye iwayini, wasenatha.
\v 26 Uyise uIsaka wasesithi kuye: Ake usondele, ungange, ndodana yami.
\v 27 Wasesondela, wamanga; wasenuka iphunga lezembatho zakhe, wambusisa\x + Heb. 11.20.\x* wathi: Khangela, iphunga lendodana yami linjengephunga lensimu\x + Hos. 14.6.\x* iN\nd kosi\nd* eyibusisileyo.
\v 28 Ngakho uNkulunkulu akunike okwamazolo amazulu lokokuvunda komhlaba\x + Dute. 33.13,28. 2 Sam. 1.21.\x*, lenala yamabele lewayini elitsha\x + Dute. 33.28.\x*.
\v 29 Abantu kabakukhonze, lezizwe zikukhothamele. Bana yinkosi yabafowenu\x + 2 Sam. 8.14.\x*, lamadodana kanyoko akukhothamele\x + 49.8.\x*. Okuqalekisayo kaqalekiswe, lokubusisayo kabusiswe\x + 12.3. Nani 24.9.\x*!
\p
\v 30 Kwasekusithi uIsaka eseqedile ukubusisa uJakobe, kwathi uJakobe esanda ukuphuma phambi kukaIsaka uyise, uEsawu umnewabo wafika evela ekuzingeleni kwakhe.
\v 31 Laye futhi walungisa ukudla okumnandi, wa\add ku\add*sa kuyise; wathi kuyise: Ubaba kavuke, adle okwenyama yenyamazana yendodana yakhe, ukuze umphefumulo wakho ungibusise.
\v 32 UIsaka uyise wasesithi kuye: Ungubani? Wasesithi: Ngiyindodana yakho, izibulo lakho uEsawu.
\v 33 UIsaka wasethuthumela ngokuthuthumela okukhulukazi, wathi: Pho, ngubani\x + Jobe 9.24.\x* ozingele inyama yenyamazana wa\add yi\add*letha kimi, ngasengisidla okwayo yonke ungakafiki? Ngimbusisile, yebo uzabusiswa.
\v 34 Kwathi uEsawu esezwe amazwi kayise, wakhala ngokukhala okukhulu lokubuhlungu isibili\x + Heb. 12.17.\x*, wathi kuyise: Ngibusisa lami njalo, baba!
\v 35 Wasesithi: Umfowenu ufike ngenkohliso, wathatha isibusiso sakho.
\v 36 Wasesithi: Kasikuthi babiza ibizo lakhe \add ngokuthi\add* nguJakobe\x + 25.26.\x*\f + \fk uJakobe: \fl okuyikuthi, \fq umqhubekisi.\f*, ukuthi ungiqile lezizikhathi ezimbili? Ilungelo lobuzibulo bami ulithethe\x + 25.33.\x*, khangela-ke, khathesi uthethe isibusiso sami. Wathi futhi: Kawungigcinelanga mina isibusiso?
\v 37 UIsaka wasephendula wathi kuEsawu: Khangela, ngimbekile abe yinkosi phezu kwakho\x + 27.29. 2 Sam. 8.14.\x*, labo bonke abafowabo ngimnikile babe zinceku; ngimsekele ngamabele lewayini elitsha\x + 27.28.\x*; pho, ngingabe ngisakwenzelani, ndodana yami?
\v 38 UEsawu wasesithi kuyise: Ulesibusiso esisodwa yini, baba? Ngibusisa lami njalo, baba. UEsawu waphakamisa ilizwi lakhe wakhala inyembezi\x + Heb. 12.17.\x*.
\v 39 UIsaka uyise wasephendula wathi kuye: Khangela, umuzi wakho uzakuba khatshana lokuvunda komhlaba lakhatshana lamazolo amazulu avela phezulu.
\v 40 Njalo uzaphila ngenkemba yakho, uzakhonza umfowenu\x + 25.23. 2 Sam. 8.14. 1 Kho. 22.47. Obad. 18-20.\x*. Kodwa kuzakuthi lapho usuphunyuka, uzakwephula ijogwe lakhe entanyeni yakho\x + 2 Kho. 8.20-22.\x*.
\p
\v 41 UEsawu wasemzonda uJakobe ngenxa yesibusiso uyise ayembusise ngaso\x + 37.4.\x*. UEsawu wasesithi enhliziyweni yakhe: Insuku zokulilela ubaba sezisondele\x + 50.3,4,10; 50.15.\x*, khona ngizambulala umnawami uJakobe\x + Obad. 10.\x*.
\v 42 Kwathi uRebeka etshelwa amazwi kaEsawu indodana yakhe enkulu, wathuma wabiza uJakobe indodana yakhe encinyane, wathi kuye: Khangela, uEsawu umnewenu uyaziduduza ngawe ukuthi akubulale.
\v 43 Ngakho khathesi, ndodana yami, lalela ilizwi lami; sukuma uzibalekele uye kuLabani umfowethu eHarani\x + 11.31; 24.4; 29.4.\x*,
\v 44 njalo uhlale laye insuku ezinlutshwana, ize idede intukuthelo yomnewenu,
\v 45 kuze kuthi ulaka lomnewenu ludede kuwe, futhi akhohlwe lokho okwenze kuye; besengithuma ngikulande khona; kungani ngizalahlekelwa layini lobabili ngosuku lunye?
\p
\v 46 URebeka wasesithi kuIsaka: Nginengekile yimpilo ngenxa yamadodakazi kaHethi\x + 26.35; 28.8.\x*; uba uJakobe ethatha umfazi kumadodakazi kaHethi anjengala, emadodakazini alelilizwe\x + 24.3.\x*, ngiphilelani?
